The player will be able to run, and jump. Contact with enemies will result in the players death and the game will restart.
The player will collect gems that can be used to purchase upgrades. One such upgrading being increased speed. 
The upgrades will get more expensive with each purchase. 
The game scene will get increasenly more difficult with obstacles to jump on/ over
Falling when there is no ground under the player will result in the player's death and the game restarting. 
